cs.CY, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.DL, cs.DB

Reasoning: 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is the most likely category as the paper discusses the societal benefits of centralised data provision for electricity system modelling. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper mentions the use of machine learning algorithms for data processing. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is a possibility as the paper discusses the benefits of improving transparency and reproducibility in electricity system modelling. 
- cs.DL (Digital Libraries) is another possibility as the paper describes the Open Power System Data platform as a method for collecting, checking, processing, aggregating, documenting and publishing data. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is also a possibility as the paper discusses the quality of input data used in electricity system modelling.
